ATTN TX: @GovAbbott has issued a State Disaster Declaration for Texas Coastal areas expected to be impacted by severe weather &amp; flooding by Hurricane Hanna. For all Texans in those areas, please continue to heed local weather warnings. https://twitter.com/govabbott/status/1287148693150470144 QT @GovAbbott State Disaster Declaration issued for 32 counties as Hurricane Hanna makes landfall on the Texas Coast. 

Texans in the #RGV, Coastal Bend, and surrounding areas are urged to follow the guidance from local officials and take shelter immediately. 

